{HOBBY
The Hobby is easily identified by its black moustache and "kikikiki" or "kew" voice. It flys at dusk mostly catching flying insects,even though its a meat eater. Its prey is mostly Swallows and Larks, it is mostly known by dropping food from one to another. This is the most intresting bird in our area.
